{"word":"G3935 - παρίημι - paríēmi - par-ee'-ay-mi - Hang down","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρίημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paríēmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ee'-ay-mi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hang down</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நெகிழ்"},{"paragraph":"1. to let pass; to pass by, neglect"},{"paragraph":"2. to relax, loosen, let go"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <b>&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b>  <b>hie&#x0304;mi</b> (to <i>send</i>); to <i>let by</i>, that is, <i>relax:</i> - hang down.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3929/3929\">G3929</a>, <a href=\"#/G3935/3935\">G3935</a>, <a href=\"#/G859/859\">G859</a>, <a href=\"#/G863/863\">G863</a>"}]}